{"tid":1740610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候將火力放翻上文宣","createTime":"2019-11-20T03:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T15:35:45.000Z","uid":171668,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e44c2622499282963f713f370fe9641355e93433","tid":1740610,"uid":171668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:55:24.000Z","msg":"對家文宣火力全開<br />\n必須要有行動反制！<br />\n不過有一點，佢地永遠都贏唔到我地<br />\n就係佢地無錢就唔會做野<br />\n<br />\n選舉臨近<br />\n我地應該集中火力<br />\n排山倒海文宣！"},{"pid":"46f57ecdeb3f9df240c5a74e1a47032c80250014","tid":1740610,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:57:46.000Z","msg":"喂文宣真係好緊要！尤其經過呢兩間大學圍城之後，身邊好多藍絲變咗做黃，佢哋真係可以再教育的，唔好放棄呢啲潛力隊友。好多而家都識講話共產黨根本想殺曬兩代年青人，佢哋開始擔心燒到自己果疊，我諗文宣方向可以諗諗殺兩代人呢個要點。"},{"pid":"4da9e89c319b87403c2a745948fbe8134a342c86","tid":1740610,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:02:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d11685331f94ed2d283f435ae7eb01cf2730fcc9","tid":1740610,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:04:12.000Z","msg":"【制裁名單】重推香港人權及民主法案Wishlist<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1740529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1740529</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"460d1cb681f81a0f89d7f0499b69f16587454cda","tid":1740610,"uid":272030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:04:17.000Z","msg":"泛民區議會選舉前快啲做野<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737778</a><br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫手推"},{"pid":"b9470dda4a0a8c1214acb8979e0eb8ec585de7c6","tid":1740610,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:04:38.000Z","msg":"[神獸召喚] 繼鶳之後，再出另一隻神獸 -- 靜靜雞<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eyJJRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eyJJRS</a>"},{"pid":"c7c6ae8101f8fff5814aa01fbf2229778fd74b4a","tid":1740610,"uid":272030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc